sep.gaia.resources.markeroption

Class MarkerStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.markeroption.MarkerStorage

  • public class MarkerStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is to store MarkerResource into and load MarkerResource out of a specific file which in the methods of this class will be referred to as POI-File. It is called by the MarkerResourceManager when new markers are to be stored or existing markers are to be loaded.
    Author:
    Michael Mitterer, Fabian Buske
